==Russian==

===Noun===
'''кофе''' (kófe) {{m}} {{indeclinable}}

# [[coffee]] (''beverage'')
#*[[чёрный]] кофе — black coffee
#*кофе с [[молоко|молоком]] — milk coffee, white coffee
#*[[крепкий]] кофе — strong coffee
# coffee (''seeds'')
#*кофе в [[зерно|зёрнах]] — whole beans coffee
#*[[молотый]] кофе — ground coffee
#*[[растворимый]] кофе — instant coffee
#*кофе без [[кофеин|кофеина]] — decaf

====Usage notes====
#Although the word '''кофе''' is indeclinable, it carries masculine gender. Yet informally it is often used in neuter gender, which can be seen in declension of adjectives, for example, "''[[горячий|горячее]] кофе''". Such usage is usually frowned upon by educated people.
#Colloquially '''кофе''' may sometimes be declined into cases, usually for humorous effect: "''[[налить]] кофю''" (partitive) — to pour some coffee; "''[[нет]] кофя''" (genitive) — there is no coffee; "''[[угостить]] кофем''" (instrumental) — to serve coffee.
#As the lack of declension is inconvenient, the diminutive forms of '''кофе''', notably [[кофеёк]] and [[кофей]], are often used.

